{"sections":[{"kind":"hero","backgroundImage":"ic_theme_intro.png","title":"Going further with more resources","chapter":"Go further with more ressources","image":"ic_theme_intro.png","estimatedTimeInMinutes":10,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since you have learnt how OUDS works with theme, themeable view, components, tuning and vieww modifiers, it is time now to discover some online resources."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"tasks":[{"anchor":"More-resources","stepsSection":[{"type":"step","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The iOS technical documentation is available online. It has been generated from all the Swift DocC documentation written in the Swift Package."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You will find several catalogs (as many as librairies) with details about everyhting: components, tokens, themes, providers, etc."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can get it at "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],"code":null,"media":"tutorial-6-1.png","runtimePreview":null},{"type":"step","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The whole design system is documented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"icon finder","type":"text"}]},{"text":" is also available there to get icons for your projects.","type":"text"}]}],"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Go to the website and learn things at ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]}],"code":null,"media":"tutorial-6-2.png","runtimePreview":null},{"type":"step","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS iOS provides a